net.cloud.server.util.function

Class ConsumerFilter<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.cloud.server.util.function.ConsumerFilter<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the accept method parameter
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Consumer<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    WorldPlayerMap.LoggedInFilter

    public abstract class ConsumerFilter<T>
extends Object
implements Consumer<T>
    A Consumer that can be used for filtering the function applications. The accept() method must still be specified, and should call passFilter() if the call should be forwarded to the composed Consumer.
